  <brief_title>Vitamin D3 Supplementation in Dialysis Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Placebo-Controlled, Double Blind Study Evaluating the Effect of Cholecalciferol on Vasoactive Hormones, Heart Function, Arterial Stiffness, and Blood Pressure in Dialysis Patients.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
